body:
It would be nice if someone could test the examples of https://github.com/rust-windowing/glutin. The normal window example can be run with `cargo run --example window`, though the following diff needs to be applied first:

```diff
diff --git a/glutin_examples/examples/window.rs b/glutin_examples/examples/window.rs
index f7da6c4..40b0c05 100644
--- a/glutin_examples/examples/window.rs
+++ b/glutin_examples/examples/window.rs
@@ -7,7 +7,7 @@ use glutin::ContextBuilder;
 
 fn main() {
     let el = EventLoop::new();
-    let wb = WindowBuilder::new().with_title("A fantastic window!");
+    let wb = WindowBuilder::new().with_title("A fantastic window!").with_maximized(true);
 
     let windowed_context =
         ContextBuilder::new().build_windowed(wb, &el).unwrap();
```

If that doesn't work, this needs to be reported to winit.
